To read our policy on gifts  please go here  To make a book or financial donation please contact Preston Library at 540 464 7228  Preston Library has an active Friends organization which sponsors and hosts programs and invites membership to the organization  Over the years  contributions to the Friends have made significant additions  and enhancements to library resources  services  and facilities  All contributions to Friends support library needs  For information about the Friends of Preston Library and for information about how to give  click on the above Friends of Preston Library link or contact the library at 540 464 7228  VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 